♪Deep down inside♪

7
00:00:52,760 --> 00:00:55,220
♪What I felt♪

8
00:00:55,430 --> 00:00:57,800
♪Was nothing but pain♪

9
00:00:57,890 --> 00:01:01,690
♪My only wish was♪

10
00:01:02,100 --> 00:01:05,310
♪Our souls could connect♪

11
00:01:08,100 --> 00:01:13,100
♪Now we’ve stopped dreaming♪

12
