740
00:45:44,280 --> 00:45:45,360
He’s your father.

741
00:45:47,070 --> 00:45:48,230
You shouldn’t have hit him.

742
00:45:49,400 --> 00:45:50,150
You can cure him,

743
00:45:51,030 --> 00:45:51,550
