774
00:48:25,470 --> 00:48:26,770
♪Just like sometimes♪

775
00:48:26,770 --> 00:48:28,080
♪I get caught up in fear for no reason♪

776
00:48:28,080 --> 00:48:29,100
♪Sunlight we take granted for♪

777
00:48:29,100 --> 00:48:30,880
